    "Name": "Corvis",
    "Details": "This variant was produced during the Jihad era in 3075, utilizing new technologies. The original's UAC/10 has been replaced by a Class 20 Hyper-Assault Gauss Rifle with three tons of ammunition. The left arm-mounted medium pulse lasers were similarly replaced with heavy medium lasers. The 'Mech's accuracy has been improved with the addition of a targeting computer mounted in the left torso.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Modular Weapons</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.08</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Right Lower</color>",
